      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">Free AI Builders:<span class="block text-[#F5521A]">What's the Catch?</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mt-6">The honest truth about "free" AI website builders.</p>
