        <p class="text-sm">Every "free" AI builder limits you to force an upgrade. The free tier is a trial, not a product. You're testing on borrowed time.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">The Hidden Costs of "Free"</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Free sounds great until you realize what you're actually paying with. Here's what free tiers really cost:
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-4">
