          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Read the privacy policies. Your content, visitor data, and user behavior train their AI models. Nothing's freeâ€”you're paying with data.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-4">
