          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Subdomains rank worse than custom domains. yoursite.wixsite.com vs yoursite.comâ€”Google knows which one is a real business. Free tiers handicap your search visibility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- UNEXPECTED FINDINGS -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-amber-50 border-[3px] border-yellow-300 p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Unexpected Findings From Testing 31 Free AI Builders</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">What nobody tells you about free tiers</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-yellow-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">"Unlimited pages" is a half-truth</p>
