      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">The Bottom Line</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Free AI builders are great for testing. They let you try platforms risk-free, experiment with prompts, and see results in minutes. Use them for validation, learning, and side projects.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        But for anything seriousâ€”anything with revenue potential, client work, or long-term goalsâ€”free tiers are false economy. The $15/month saves you hours of frustration, lost revenue, and eventual migration pain.
